Name: H-SNIPER: Middle East
About the game: HENTAI SNIPER: Middle East In this first-person sniper shooter our special H.E.N.T.A.I. Agent has received the most dangerous and difficult task possible: clear out the ruins of once city from terrorists. STORY There is nothing left of what was once a city. Nowadays it is an abandoned, heavily guarded by terrorists territory. Not once before we were able to come this close to their base. This is our best chance to fight them back.. for the H.E.N.T.A.I.! KEY FEATURES Shooting game based on sniper mechanics User-friendly and simple controls A variety of satisfying animations Wishlist the game and be the first one to win the terrorists over! /
